reviewText: Really BAD video quality. Oh and it's in a foreign language with no closed captions.
This video is the same as one that is available for free. And it is not from 2007 as the description says. Estonia looks wonderful, but there is no reason to pay for this old film.
Quick peek at Tallin and parts of Estonia.
Clear and bright picture quality. Good narrative. Good history of area. Very pleased with quality and service. Great addition to my library.
